<div class="landingpage">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="col-xs-12 herounit">
      <div class="herounit-content">
        <%= image_tag("spendit.png", class: 'img-responsive herounit-image') %>
        <h2 class="open-sans">Tracking your <%= image_tag('expenses.png', class: 'img-responsive expense-logo') %>  is easy!</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container about-container">
    <h2 class="">About</h2>
    <p class="lead ">
      we have experienced group based budget problem and got an idea why don't we solve it. I hope most of them might have issues like this.<br><br> If so this app is for us.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="feature" id="feature">
  <div class="container feature-budget">
    <h2 class="">Fix your budget</h2>
    <p class="lead ">
      Update your budget for the month and start spending it.
    </p>
    <br>
    <h2 class="">Create Tasklist of expenses</h2>
    <p class="lead">
      Create a tasklist which repeats everymonth to track your basic Expenses like Rent, Internet Bill, Dish Bill and EMI's with specfied amount of time.
    </p>
    <br>
    <h2 class="">Group Budget Expenses</h2>
    <p class="lead">
      You can track your Group expenses especially when you are staying with friends.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about" id="contact">
  <div class="container about-container">
    <h2 class="">Contact</h2>
    <h4 class="">
      Developer: Prasanna Vijayan<br><br>
      Email: <a href="mailto:prasannavijayan446@gmail.com">Prasanna Vijayan</a><br><br>
      Twitter: @PrasannaVijayan
    </h4>
  </div>
</section>

